.\}
Inside the project, create an HDL card with the name
\fBmycard\fR\&. The HDL card definition named
\fBmycard\&.xml\fR
will be placed in the subdirectory
\fBhdl/cards/specs/\fR:
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
ocpidev create hdl card mycard
.fi
.if n \{\
.RE
.\}
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04' 2.\h'+01'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
