.\}
Inside the project, delete an HDL card definition named
\fBmycard\&.xml\fR
from a project\(cqs
\fBhdl/cards/specs/\fR
subdirectory:
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
ocpidev delete hdl card mycard
.fi
